<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Akashism</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #4e54c8, #8f94fb);
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            color: #ffeb3b;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #ffcc00;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: left;
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
        }
        .mantra {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .shapath {
            font-style: italic;
            padding: 10px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffeb3b;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Akashism</h1>
    <h2>Akash Premi Ki Shapath</h2>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Main Akash ka ek ansh hoon – mukt anant aur joda hua. Main na koi seema dekhta hoon, na ghrina, na vibhajan. Main akash ke neeche chalta hoon, aur prem mere andar basta hai.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <h2>Akashism Ke Siddhant</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Akash Ka Adhikar:</strong> Har insaan akash ka hissa hai – sabka samman karo.</li>
            <li><strong>Saath Chalna:</strong> Nature aur community ke saath jud ke jeeyo.</li>
            <li><strong>Mahaakash Se Seekh:</strong> Cosmos se wisdom aur humility lo.</li>
            <li><strong>Akash Ka Karam:</strong> Sky ne jo diya — uska dhyaan rakho.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <h2>Akash Mantra</h2>
        <div class="mantra">
            Om Akashaya Namah
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="shapath">
        <p>Main Akash ka ek ansh hoon – mukt anant aur joda hua. Main na koi seema dekhta hoon, na ghrina, na vibhajan. Main akash ke neeche chalta hoon, aur prem mere andar basta hai.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
